**IMPORTANT:** Your template selections should support these macro-level directives:
- **Energy targets** indicate intensity levels (HIGH/PEAK = aggressive/dramatic, MED/BUILD = balanced/rising, LOW/RELEASE = subtle/ambient)
- **Motion density** guides activity level (BUSY = fast/complex, MED = balanced, SPARSE = slow/simple)
- **Choreography style** indicates visual approach (IMAGERY = narrative, ABSTRACT = patterns, HYBRID = mixed)
- **Palette** indicates color theme override for the section (if specified, choose templates that complement this mood)
- **Motifs** indicate visual patterns emphasized in this section (use to inform template geometry/movement choices)
